Package: exposuretemplate
Type: Package
Title: TEMPLATE for ZCTA/County-Level Exposure Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: TEMPLATE. Replace {exposure} throughout with your exposure name.
    Provides functions to fetch, summarize, and map ZCTA- and county-level
    exposure data. Processed data is hosted on Zenodo; get_data() downloads
    and caches only the requested slice.
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/UChicago-ExtremeWeather/exposuretemplate
